# BRAND PROJECTS — PRIVATE BY DEFAULT.
# Every brand under projects/ contains the user's confidential strategy,
# buyer personas, palette decisions, brand book, and generated assets.
# These are personal/business data. Do NOT version them in this public repo.
# (Keep an empty projects/.gitkeep so the directory structure exists for new users.)
projects/*
!projects/.gitkeep

# Higgsfield bundled skills — owned by Higgsfield, installed by the user
# via `npx skills add higgsfield-ai/skills`. The CMO repo references them via
# symlinks under .claude/skills/, which the install command recreates.
.agents/

# Evals workspace (regenerable, per-developer)
.claude/skills/*-workspace/

# OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Claude Code session artifacts
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/settings.local.json
